Message:
Gotcha, tiny Master~!
And you, sad Master—
I’m gonna give you
a biiig hug, okay?

Hey, smiley Master
and shiny Master!
Hold hands with me,
and let’s play swingy-swing~

With so many Masters,
we can play a lot
and have tons of fun!

But, how did you make
more of yourself, Master?

‘Cause you’re a grown-up?
Oh, that’s why!
Grown-ups are so amazing, huh!

Alright, all together now...
Nina’s Special...High Fiiive!
Oh, I can’t reach you, giant Master.

Hey, upside-down Master,
can you carry me...?
Yesss, this’ll do it...
